Package: scrcpy-gui
Version: 1.3
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3-pyside6.qtcore, python3-pyside6.qtgui, python3-pyside6.qtwidgets
Maintainer: Scrcpy GUI Team <maintainer@example.com>
Description: A simple PySide6 GUI for ADB WiFi connections and scrcpy
 Scrcpy GUI provides an easy-to-use interface for:
 - Connecting to Android devices over WiFi using ADB
 - Managing wireless pairing (Android 11+)
 - Starting and controlling scrcpy screen mirroring
 - Supports both English and Russian languages
 - Includes bundled adb and scrcpy binaries
